description:
Welcome all to the November SWmobile Talk Night 🗣 🎉

Talk 1: Chaos Mode - David Branton
Talk 2: Real world testing with BDD & Espresso - Dimitris Karavias
Talk 3: From Beer Making to Corporate Bliss via a Failed Startup - Matthew Hazley

We'll be hosted by JustEat who will very kindly be providing food and drink on the evening.

Doors will open at 18:30pm
- Food and drink will be available.
- Talks will start at 19:00 with interlude ~19:45
- We aim to be finished by 21:00

After the event, we'll move on to a near by pub to continue the discussions. 🍷

If you do have a talk that you'd like to present at a future meetup then please do get in touch via http://cfp.swmobile.org
title: November Talk Night 🗣
